name: Two China Eastern A330-243s Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
In the summer, China Eastern operates two daily flights into Vancouver, both by the Airbus A330-200. Here we have the evening flight arriving, operated by B-5975, landing runway 26R and exiting at M6, and the morning flight arriving the next day operated by B-5968 and once again landing 26R and exiting at M6. ATC is included for both, enjoy!

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

FLIGHT INFO
Airline: China Eastern (CES/MU)
Aircraft: Airbus A330-200 (A332)
Aircraft Name: None
Livery: Standard
Engines: 2x RR Trent 772C-60 (each)
Registration: B-5975 and B-5968
Route: PVG-YVR (both)
Callsign: China Eastern 590 and China Eastern 581
Runway used: 26R (both)
Local Time: 2000 and 1000
